=== DESIGN DECISIONS ===

- superadmin has full CRUD and role administration.
- admin handles metadata, asset uploads/deletes, and moderation.
- employee can insert/upload and edit, but cannot delete.
- user can read content and manage only their own comments and reading history.

=== R2 DELIVERY ===

- Free assets are served through a public CDN path.
- Premium assets require a short-lived HMAC-signed URL.
- The Worker validates the signature before the object is read from R2.

